Each author has his own personal style of writing. 
And some set of words is found most often in each work of this author. 
The comparison of such sets of words is used as one of the methods of detecting plagiarism. 
So, I found out what interesting words are most often found in the works of Joan Rowling. 
During my work I have used libraries to work with pdf-files from collections, algorithms for decoding and frequency counting.
